blondetron walks out, sad as ever that the man she thought was rex was really 
a destron in diguise. Shredder seemed to have no interrest in her at that 
time. she runs back into the room. "Shredder, why dont you like me? Is it 
mantella your after?" she asks. if it was, she'd have to find a way to kill 
her, even if it meant sleeping with magnatron to get him on her side.
